| POST | `/api/messages/threads/{id}/messages` | Send message |
| POST | `/api/messages/threads/{id}/messages/image` | Send image |
| **GET** | **`/api/messages/threads/{id}/poll?after=ISO8601`** | Poll for new messages |
| DELETE | `/api/messages/threads/{id}/messages/{msgId}` | Delete own message |

The **polling endpoint** (line 110-118):
